The chimpanzee was now crossing a large African plain, knuckles on the ground 
as he went at a pace that wasn't walking, but wasn't running.  He stopped, 
seeing the Cybertronian Fire.  In his current form, it looked as big as 
Cybertron, and it looked like it was covered in weapons.

He dropped to the ground.
